OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778148401
OL,3,CCCTV captures gang stealing life-
OL,4,Csaving equipment from fire station
OL,6,FCCTV footage has revealed the moment a
OL,7,Fgang raided a fire station to steal
OL,8,Femergency cutting equipment used to
OL,9,Fsave lives.
OL,11,FThe gang - consisting of twins Carl
OL,12,Fand Lee Kettle, 40, and 45-year-old
OL,13,FBarry Dillon from Liverpool - pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to conspiracy to commit
OL,15,Fburglary and conspiracy to steal.
OL,17,FThe trio appeared before Liverpool
OL,18,FCrown Court following an intensive 18-
OL,19,Fmonth investigation into a conspiracy
OL,20,Fthat targeted cash machines and
OL,21,Femergency services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
