OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778148401
OL,3,CCCTV captures gang stealing life-
OL,4,Csaving equipment from fire station
OL,6,FBetween January 2020 and April 2025,
OL,7,Fthe group stole from supermarkets and
OL,8,Fpetrol stations across the UK in a
OL,9,Fstring of "sophisticated" attacks.
OL,11,FIn addition to the cash machine raids,
OL,12,Fthe gang focused on stealing high-
OL,13,Fpowered cars and vital emergency
OL,14,Fcutting equipment from fire stations
OL,15,Fin Merseyside, Cheshire, Greater
OL,16,FManchester and Nottinghamshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
