OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778148401
OL,3,CCCTV captures gang stealing life-
OL,4,Csaving equipment from fire station
OL,6,FAt the sentencing, the Kettle twins
OL,7,Fwere both jailed for six years and
OL,8,Feight months. Meanwhile, Dillon was
OL,9,Fsentenced to three years and eight
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FDavid Brunskill, who led the
OL,13,Finvestigation, described the operation
OL,14,Fas "well-planned," noting the
OL,15,Fsignificant damage caused to local
OL,16,Fbusinesses and cost to the public to
OL,17,Freplace equipment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
