CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778148401
OL,3,CCCTV captures gang stealing life-
OL,4,Csaving equipment from fire station
OL,6,FHe said: "This meant the supermarket
OL,7,Fnot only losing thousands of pounds of
OL,8,Fmoney but also costly repairs to the
OL,9,Fbuilding and replacing the cash
OL,10,Fmachines.
OL,12,F"They also stole emergency cutting
OL,13,Fequipment from fire stations...This
OL,14,Fwas also an expense to the public
OL,15,Fpurse to replace such items."
OL,17,FGed Sheridan, Assistant Chief Fire
OL,18,FOfficer at Merseyside Fire and Rescue,
OL,19,Fwarned that the gang's actions had put
OL,20,Flives at risk.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
