PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778148401
OL,3,CCCTV captures gang stealing life-
OL,4,Csaving equipment from fire station
OL,6,F"Every piece of equipment on a fire
OL,7,Fengine is there for a reason - to help
OL,8,Fus save lives", he said.
OL,10,F"Stealing emergency service equipment
OL,11,Ffrom fire stations risks preventing
OL,12,Ffirefighters from helping someone in a
OL,13,Flife-threatening situation.
OL,15,F"We welcome the sentencing and hope it
OL,16,Fsends a clear message that crimes
OL,17,Fagainst emergency services endanger
OL,18,Fthe public."
